95
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:49,800
You want to, don't you?.

96
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:58,500
Let's go in the office.

97
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:08,000
Where?. On the floor?.
What kind of a girl do you think am l?.

98
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:13,800
