115
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,600
Put them down!

116
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:02,200
Is it a good smell?.

117
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,600
Not inordinately.

118
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:53,000
Did you hear that?.
- It's the fireworks.

119
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:58,500
I'd better go check. Make sure
she's OK. - Your mother?.

120
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:04,100
Will you just stay here?.
