- I don't mind being bothered.

214
00:26:46,700 --> 00:26:48,100
Thank you, Mrs. Lane.

215
00:26:56,600 --> 00:27:00,100
Let's get back to "Talk of the Town"
with Fran Ambrose.

216
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:04,500
